data.description: What a yard! Two living areas, 3 bed 2 bath home sitting on a corner lot with mature pecan tree and other large trees. The back yard is very large (almost acre) and is fully fenced with chain link offering plenty of room for the kids or pets. The larger of the living areas has a fireplace for those cozy nights just relaxing with family. Don't let this one slide by your radar call today for your showing.
